The Fairmont Mount Kenya Safari Club recently hosted top celebrities and personalities for a limitless travel experience to launch the Accor Live Limitless lifestyle programme. The experiences included Hennessy pairing dinner at the newly launched restaurant Colobus, followed by lunch at the terrace by the beautiful gardens. Guests woke up to Moet and Chandon champagne breakfast by the slopes of Mount Kenya and ended the day with a bush dinner on top of the Likki River and all followed by a day of relaxation at the Mount Kenya Riuki Spa.